Text: 'I went to Unplanned leh ladhak trip with my Three more friends to whom i meet
  first time. The trip started from Delhi on 15 june 2017 and we take a car I10 for
  ladhak rather then SUV or any heavy motor

  Our first stoppage was  Patnitop were we reached at 5 pm then after sight seeing,
  we take a rest for night and at next morning we depart for our second stop that
  was Srinagar in the kasmir valley,  surly it is a paradise of Earth,'
